## ğŸ”· Step 3: Equation of Perpendicular Line Through A(3,5)

Using point-slope form:

y - 5 = -1(x - 3)

Expanding:

y - 5 = -x + 3  
y = -x + 8  

Rewriting:

x + y = 8

---

## ğŸ”· Step 4: Find Intersection with Mirror Line

Mirror line:

